Achievements.Name: Maze High (Score)
Achievements.Description: Beat the high score on all Pacopolis (Chapter 1) levels.

Achievements.Name: Bursting Bubbles
Achievements.Description: Beat the high score on all Paclantis (Chapter 2) levels.

Achievements.Name: High in the Sky
Achievements.Description: Beat the high score on all Space (Chapter 3) levels.

Achievements.Name: High Time (Travel)
Achievements.Description: Beat the high score on all Prehistoric Pac-World (Chapter 4) levels.

Achievements.Name: Lava Level Master
Achievements.Description: Beat the high score on all Netherworld (Chapter 5) levels.

Achievements.Name: Six Pac
Achievements.Description: End a level with six Health (Hearts).

Achievements.Name: Pac-ed with Skill
Achievements.Description: Complete the Tutorial and all of the Berry Challenges.

Achievements.Name: Cyli Luck
Achievements.Description: Complete any Cyli Hover Board level without losing a life.

Achievements.Name: Spiral-ing In Control
Achievements.Description: Complete any Spiral Cherry Copter level without losing a life.

Achievements.Name: Pac in Your Trash
Achievements.Description: Chomp every container in any level.

Achievements.Name: Rocket-Man
Achievements.Description: Complete the Lemon Rocket level without losing a life.

Achievements.Name: Fireball-istic
Achievements.Description: Stun 100 enemies with Fire Pac's Special attack.

Achievements.Name: Everybody Chill
Achievements.Description: Freeze 100 enemies with Ice Pac's Special attack.

Achievements.Name: Gotta Bounce!
Achievements.Description: Stun 100 enemies with Rubber Pac's Special attack.

Achievements.Name: Magnetic Personality
Achievements.Description: Attract and chomp 100 enemies using Metal Pac's magnet tongue.

Achievements.Name: BOO!
Achievements.Description: Defeat 200 Blue (Scared) Ghosts.

Achievements.Name: Rockin'!
Achievements.Description: Defeat 5 Stone Monsters as Granite Ball Pac.

Achievements.Name: Challenge Schmalenge
Achievements.Description: Successfully complete all Betrayus Challenges at least once.

Achievements.Name: Getting to Know You
Achievements.Description: Read the bios for each of Pac's friends between levels.

Achievements.Name: Life is Good!
Achievements.Description: Get the number of Pac's Lives up to 50.

Achievements.Name: Dots Incredible!
Achievements.Description: Grab 200 Pac Pellets in a single level.

Achievements.Name: Pac-ing in the Prizes
Achievements.Description: Get the Pac Prize score bonus at least once on every level.

Achievements.Name: Chatter Pac
Achievements.Description: Talk to each of Pac's friends between levels at least once.

Achievements.Name: Gold Medalist
Achievements.Description: Win a Gold Medal on every level.

Achievements.Name: Pac-Man Fever
Achievements.Description: Visit every Arcade Zone in the game.
